trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeNamespaceImport"></xref> objects.
The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeNamespaceImportCollection> class provides a simple collection object that can be used to store a set of <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeNamespaceImport> objects.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeNamespaceImportCollection"></xref> class.
Adds a <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeNamespaceImport"></xref> object to the collection.
The <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeNamespaceImport"></xref> object to add to the collection.
Adds a set of <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeNamespaceImport"></xref> objects to the collection.
An array of type <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeNamespaceImport"></xref> that contains the objects to add to the collection.
value is `null`.
Clears the collection of members.
Gets the number of namespaces in the collection.
The number of namespaces in the collection.
Gets an enumerator that enumerates the collection members.
An <xref href="System.Collections.IEnumerator"></xref> that indicates the collection members.
Gets or sets the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeNamespaceImport"></xref> object at the specified index in the collection.
The index of the collection to access.
A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeNamespaceImport"></xref> object at each valid index.
The index parameter is outside the valid range of indexes for the collection.
Copies the elements of the <xref href="System.Collections.ICollection"></xref> to an <xref href="System.Array"></xref>, starting at a particular <xref href="System.Array"></xref> index.
This member is an explicit interface member implementation.
It can be used only when the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeNamespaceImportCollection> instance is cast to an <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> interface.
The one-dimensional <xref href="System.Array"></xref> that is the destination of the elements copied from the <xref href="System.Collections.ICollection"></xref>.
The array must have zero-based indexing.
The zero-based index in array at which copying begins.
Gets the number of elements contained in the <xref href="System.Collections.ICollection"></xref>.
The number of elements contained in the <xref href="System.Collections.ICollection"></xref>.
Gets a value indicating whether access to the <xref href="System.Collections.ICollection"></xref> is synchronized (thread safe).
`true` if access to the <xref href="System.Collections.ICollection"></xref> is synchronized (thread safe); otherwise, `false`.
This property always returns `false`.
Gets an object that can be used to synchronize access to the <xref href="System.Collections.ICollection"></xref>.
An object that can be used to synchronize access to the <xref href="System.Collections.ICollection"></xref>.
This property always returns `null`.

An <xref href="System.Collections.IEnumerator"></xref> that can be used to iterate through the collection.
